<div id="tmglBody" >
	<div class="access"><a name="article"></a></div>
		
	<div class="twoThirdsThird2 gutterUnder">
		<div class="twoThirds gutter" >
			<div class="storyHead">

	<h1>The £4,000 eye implant to replace reading glasses </h1>
		
	<h2>
A revolutionary eye operation technique could allow millions of middle-aged 
  people to abandon their reading glasses. 

</h2>
	</div>
<div class="oneHalf gutter">
				<div class="story">
					<div id="storyEmbSlide">
			<div class="slideshow ssMain">
				<div class="nextPrevLayer">
							<div class="ssImg show">
