							<div class="ssImg hide">
									<img src="http://i.telegraph.co.uk/multimedia/archive/01993/eye1_1993790c.jpg" width="460" height="287" alt=" A revolutionary eye operation technique could allow millions of middle-aged people to abandon their reading glasses"/>
									<div class="artImageExtras" >
									
